  "link": "https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/cumis-counsel\/",
  "title": { "rendered": "Cumis Counsel" },
  "content": {
    "rendered": "<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<div id=\"pgc-1026-0-0\" class=\"pan&lt;a href=\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-480 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/01\/Law.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"393\" height=\"261\" srcset=\"https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/01\/Law.jpg 3008w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/01\/Law-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/01\/Law-768x511.jpg 768w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/01\/Law-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/murphlaw.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/01\/Law-272x182.jpg 272w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 393px) 100vw, 393px\" \/><\/div>\n<p class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"1\"><em style=\"font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\">Cumis<\/em><span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\"> counsel is attorneys who are hired or have been retained to represent a client in an insurance matter. \u00a0At times, the insured will express their intent to hire their own legal counsel and the insurance carrier is obligated to pay for those litigation expenses. In most scenarios, the insurer and insured agree to retain a single law firm to represent their interests.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p data-weight=\"1\"><span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\">Throughout the years, Chuckstern Murphy Law Firm has been retained to serve as <\/span><em style=\"font-size: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\">Cumis<\/em><span style=\"font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit;\">\u00a0counsel to pursue and litigate a multitude of\u00a0cases due to our highly experienced litigation counsel. We have litigated cases over a diverse area of the law and have successfully resolved all different types of complex legal issues.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"pg-1026-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\">\n<div id=\"pgc-1026-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\" data-weight=\"0.5\">\n<div id=\"panel-1026-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}\">\n<p class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">Once carriers and\/or clients have witnessed our effective trial skills, they have immediately retained us. Please contact us now if you would like to discuss retaining our firm for your matter. The following is a list of the insurance carriers that we have retained our firm:<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>West American Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Allstate Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Farmers Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Lumberman&#8217;s Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>CNA Insurance<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Lancer Insurance Services<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Compass Insurance<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Maryland Casualty Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243;][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>National American Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Allianz Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>American Empire Surplus Lines<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Golden Eagle Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Fireman&#8217;s Fund Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>20th Century Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Balboa Casualty Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Chubb Insurance Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #003366;\"><strong>Universal North America Ins. Co.<\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row triangle_shape=&#8221;no&#8221;][vc_column][vc_empty_space][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>",
    "protected": false
  },
